OL,3,CShared parental leave proposed to
OL,4,Cmodernise 'outdated' childcare rights
OL,6,FGuernsey's maternity leave
OL,7,Fentitlements are "outdated" and must
OL,8,Fbe modernised in the current political
OL,9,Fterm, according to a leading
OL,10,Fpolitician.
OL,12,FDeputy Tina Bury, President of the
OL,13,FCommittee for Employment and Social
OL,14,FSecurity (ESS), told the States that
OL,15,Fthe body wants to introduce shared
OL,16,Fparental leave to encourage both
OL,17,Fparents to take part in early
OL,18,Fchildcare.
