OL,4,Cmodernise 'outdated' childcare rights
OL,6,FShe added developing policy proposals
OL,7,Fis a key priority for the committee,
OL,8,Feven though the States initially asked
OL,9,FESS to explore its options on the
OL,10,Fissue back in 2015.
OL,12,F"In common with many western
OL,13,Feconomies, Guernsey has a low
OL,14,Fbirthrate, significantly below the
OL,15,Flevel which would be required to
OL,16,Fmaintain the size of the population
OL,17,Fwithout relying on migration," Deputy
OL,18,FBury told the States.
