OL,6,F"In that context, the Committee
OL,7,Fbelieves it's critically important
OL,8,Fthat the States take action to ensure
OL,9,Fthat Guernsey is a 'family-friendly'
OL,10,Fplace to live; to create an
OL,11,Fenvironment where families can choose
OL,12,Fto build their lives."
