OL,3,CShared parental leave proposed to
OL,4,Cmodernise 'outdated' childcare rights
OL,6,FJersey introduced shared parental
OL,7,Fleave legislation in 2020, giving both
OL,8,Fparents 52 weeks' leave after the
OL,9,Fbirth of their baby.
OL,11,FParents are paid their full salary for
OL,12,Fsix weeks of that period by their
OL,13,Femployer, with the same entitlements
OL,14,Fextended to parents who adopt and
OL,15,Fsurrogate parents.
OL,17,FIn the UK, parents may take 50 weeks
OL,18,Fof leave following a birth and be paid
OL,19,Fup to 37 weeks' pay between them.
